snippet.title: Unreal Tournament Pre-Alpha Season Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the game now at http://unrealtournament.com - We've just released the latest build of Unreal Tournament and we'd love for you to come and check it out! This is our biggest release to date and we're really excited to share it with you. We have new characters such as the Skaarj and female Necris with unlockable upgrades. The build includes three new maps, including a remake of the iconic map, Facing Worlds. We also have some great new features such as a new progression system and offline challenges.

To celebrate, we're  hosting a Capture the Flag Exhibition Tournament this Saturday, September 19th, featuring top players from around the world, and we'll be streaming the whole thing live on both http://Twitch.TV/unrealtournament and http://gaming.youtube.com/unrealtournament starting at 1:00 PM (EST).  Stop by the stream to learn how you can win fantastic prizes from Origin PC, NVIDIA, Corsair, Logitech, and more!
Download the new UT at http://unrealtournament.com. It's free!
Come and chat with us on 
Discord ► https://discord.gg/unrealtournament 
Reddit ► http://reddit.com/r/unrealtournament
